{"tid":2251982,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] 魔靈召喚 X 街霸  要犬神不要原五 (10)","createTime":"2020-10-21T07:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T08:12:12.000Z","uid":86158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86815a0401be4b65a9e914610e7509cbba2578c5","tid":2251982,"uid":86158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"魔靈召喚 Summoners War -<br />\n<br />\n來自韓國廠Com2uS<br />\n<br />\n未玩過既你可能睇完近排某D實況主玩完<br />\n<br />\n之後想試下又或者之前玩過想玩番<br />\n<br />\n--------重點---------------<br />\n1 呢隻驚好撚肝/農<br />\n<br />\n魔靈唔係出面D速食手機game<br />\n唔好諗住一步登天<br />\n如果由0開始的話 無幾個月<br />\n你係完全跟唔上本身有玩開既人<br />\n<br />\n2 原5好撚難抽<br />\n<br />\n200抽得1隻原5 呢D係正常<br />\n幾十抽就有叫好運,歐 OK?<br />\n光暗原5更係萬年一遇(有人玩左6年都無1隻光暗原5)<br />\n<br />\n3 符文&gt;角色<br />\n<br />\n我成隊光暗原5比對面三色3,4星打死<br />\non9架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一原因就係符文廢<br />\n正如第1點所講<br />\n呢隻驚有8成時間都係刷緊龍12巨12死12刷符<br />\n<br />\n4 暴走會激撚死你<br />\n暴走係其中一個ingame system<br />\n如果你隻寵有裝暴走符文套裝<br />\n係有22%機率再獲得回合<br />\n人地都係<br />\n所以點解有時人地隻寵可以連打你5-6次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------香港公會list---------<br />\n<br />\n-亞服-<br />\n光復香港<br />\n快樂戰鬥<br />\n<span class=\"maroon\"><del>叛徒</del></span><br />\n<br />\n香港實況主路小倫discord group<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/K46b9PK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FK46b9PK&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=68fe489b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/K46b9PK</a><br />\n<br />\n個group有不少持續有玩既巴打<br />\n<br />\n有問題可以入去問/交流<br />\n<br />\n雷京攻略<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/644903276399034388/688564586118643723/BJR5_Guide.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F644903276399034388%2F688564586118643723%2FBJR5_Guide.jpg&h=a8b812c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49e8f06b1c4893a1a0bec68ad9d8ccaf4def7d08","tid":2251982,"uid":86158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s